    <p xml:lang="ru">**Данная обертка над официальной версией для компьютера не проверена, не связана и не поддерживается TrueConf**</p>
        <p>Team messenger for video calling, collaboration, and secure communication.</p>
        <p>TrueConf features:</p>
            <ul>
                <li>- Ultra HD video meetings for up to 1,000 participants</li>
                <li>- High video and audio quality even despite unstable Internet connection</li>
                <li>- Advanced collaboration tools: content sharing, slideshow, remote desktop control, and much more</li>
                <li>- Team messaging</li>
                <li>- Smart video layouts</li>
                <li>- Easy contact and call history navigation</li>
                <li>- Blurring and changing a background</li>
                <li>- AI-based noise suppression</li>
            </ul>
  </description>
